    "description": {
      "public": "<p><em>Some heroes become legends because of their armaments. Others become legends in spite of it.</em></p><p>1d6+STR Bludgeoning.</p><p><strong>Ladlor's Tenacity.</strong> (Req. a daring spirit) The first time each encounter you would gain Dying, set your HP to 1 and gain the following benefits for 2 turns:</p><ul><li>Add LVL to damage</li><li>Immunity to all damage</li><li>Ignore rushed attacks</li></ul><hr><p>Legendary Ladle</p><p><strong>Cost:</strong> Win it from Ladlor in a contest</p>",
